ArtyTorrent Pack 94-Digital Breaks 140-149bpm-WAV samples
---------------------------------------------------------

A collection of breakbeat drum loops ranging from 140-149 bpm. These are funky loops mainly made with electronic drumkits, with heavy compression and digital effects processing. Great for emulating Fatboy Slim, Chemical Brothers, Prodigy etc.

Torrent contains 10 RAR files with 136 loops
--------------------------------------------
Breaks Kit 19 140 (12 loops)
Breaks Kit 24 145 (4)
Breaks Kit 42 145 (12)
Breaks Kit 48 140 (8)
ChFire Breaks 140-149 (9)
Funky Beats 148 (7)
Machine Language Strange 140-149 (6)
Misc Digital Breaks 140-149 (57)
Punked Up 146 (13)

Samples are from a variety of sources including CDs by EastWest, Sony/Sonic Foundry, Future Music magazine, and Loopology/Syntrillium and have all been normalized and acidized as 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz. Approx tempo is included in each filename.
